{"tha-ap482:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap482:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap482:0.3":"10 Pulinacankamiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap482:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap482:1.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap482:1.3":"Vatamigam gavesanto, ","tha-ap482:1.4":"cankamam addasam aham. ","tha-ap482:2.1":"Ucchangena pulinam gayha, ","tha-ap482:2.2":"cankame okirim aham; ","tha-ap482:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap482:2.4":"sugatassa sirimato. ","tha-ap482:3.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap482:3.2":"pulinam okirim aham; ","tha-ap482:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap482:3.4":"pulinassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap482:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap482:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap482:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap482:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap482:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap482:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap482:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap482:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap482:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap482:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pulinacankamiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap482:8.1":"Pulinacankamiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap482:9.1":"Nalamalivaggo atthacattalisamo. ","tha-ap482:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap482:11.1":"Nalamali manidado, ","tha-ap482:11.2":"ukkasatikabijani; ","tha-ap482:11.3":"Kummaso ca kusattho ca, ","tha-ap482:11.4":"giripunnagiyopi ca. ","tha-ap482:12.1":"Vallikaro panadhido, ","tha-ap482:12.2":"atho pulinacankamo; ","tha-ap482:12.3":"Gathayo pancanavuti, ","tha-ap482:12.4":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. "}